<span>1.2. </span><span>Properties</span></a><span> </span></p>
<p><span>Number </span><span>2 in</span><span> the image above is related with properties. </span><span>In this section there are predefined UI Components like dropdown, radio button or slider to filter the data. There is only one possible choice for every component. After selection the results and the facets are updated accordingly. </span></p>
<p><span>&#xa0;</span></p>
<p class="Heading-2">
