<p><span>&#xa0;</span></p><br />
<span>1.3. </span><span>Free text search with Autocomplete</span></a></p>
<p><span>The free text search</span><span>, number </span><span>3 in</span><span> the image above,</span><span> works as in any common search engine</span><span>.</span><span> It includes Autocomplete where words or phrases are being predicted once three letters or figures are entered. It supports also different languages.</span></p>
